<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Login Request {{ hostname }}</title>
        <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Login Request {{ hostname }}</h1>
        <p>Hello {{ name }}</p>
        <p>Someone requested to login with your eMail on my ticket system.</p>
        <p>If you didn't plan to login, just ignore this mail or answer the bot and let me blacklist the eMail.</p>
        <p>Otherwise go to <a href="https://{{ hostname }}/email-login/{{ oneTime }}">the login</a>.</p>
        <p>Have a great day,<br/>Your Ticket-Bot</p>
        <br />
        <p>The site {{ hostname }} is hosted and operated by Björn 'Idrinth' Büttner, see the <a href="https://{{ hostname }}/imprint">imprint</a> for more information.</p>
        <br />
        <p>If you don't want to recieve any additional mail from the site, you can blacklist your email with the attached unsubscribe information. Please note, that that will cause logins to be impossible when using this eMail.</p>
        <p>If you want to get rid of the watched ticket information mails, remove the opt-in in your profile.</p>
    </body>
</html>